{"tid":1130010,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"最近我係樓上書店到打工","createTime":"2019-04-28T17:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T18:57:00.000Z","uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fedc156549f1b8390e308d23a8a9723e716e6743","tid":1130010,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"每日都覺得被人視姦咁<br />\n有個肥毒撚日日都坐係櫃台對面既位<br />\n<br />\n佢一定幻想緊用條又粗又熱既野玷汙我<br />\n等我幫佢含撚<br />\n<br />\n然後用狗仔式抽插我下面<br />\n獲得征服感<br />\n<br />\n最後再將熱辣辣既精液一口氣射入我裡面滿足佢既佔有慾<br />\n<br />\n真係好變態<br />\n每次比錢個陣仲特登摸一下我隻手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0G8vvQG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0G8vvQG.png&h=fa9fdcd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbcf1778ed705d7aa2dcb6eef9939c298f390b5a","tid":1130010,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:44:27.000Z","msg":"扯左"},{"pid":"ff5c949fa375b2d610a5a04ea43eef44966d86a3","tid":1130010,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:48:51.000Z","msg":"梳 我聽日唔會再咁明目張膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb935abdb6893bd7659078dfd45f1c32d98ce13","tid":1130010,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bz7wfjE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBz7wfjE.png&h=cb3ebe47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就是個肥仔"},{"pid":"f507fb7a21beef08aff1e143c7120ddb46bc1b92","tid":1130010,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"本貼含有8%動漫成份"},{"pid":"d89c5d233b5192abffd3a0295a5522d183a5638f","tid":1130010,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"0dc27ceef13b93903b1fef4a63d3720cb620b2da","tid":1130010,"uid":150609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:57:22.000Z","msg"